{"tid":1079003,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"無論事隔多年我也心跳　最後和你雖如我那所料","createTime":"2019-03-26T15:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T15:20:33.000Z","uid":36497,"like":28,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"aa217462eba2fd7016cfe03e3fb037f7572137b7","tid":1079003,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:42:26.000Z","msg":"先挑引我的人愛得比我少　然後見面更少<br />\n讓我多謝你那幾秒　往後和每位也差些少<br />\n彷彿我的心　如不見了<br />\n然而懷念當日你我這段傻事　便知她　算了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WAt14in.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWAt14in.jpg&h=ed7214c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n忘掉被你感動卻也心跳<br />\n往後情侶一如每次所料<br />\n我愛的不少　遺憾也不過是<br />\n並沒法使我的心這樣跳"},{"pid":"38ffeef4dea14e6541799f9a6ab949adedb098ed","tid":1079003,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c204bf278136220feea80788afe14a731d9a810f","tid":1079003,"uid":7715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"算啦"},{"pid":"06124bdba7bd0b47f3d88bf34fef22e4f50604e0","tid":1079003,"uid":33425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:51:33.000Z","msg":"苦"},{"pid":"b4a7bf1b08c22087d8afb22b244e4ed1295f3fe0","tid":1079003,"uid":58811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:58:44.000Z","msg":"依首真係好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffc9b2f96574a3c233254aa5b2584d886ece42a","tid":1079003,"uid":243093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c204bf278136220feea80788afe14a731d9a810f","tid":1079003,"uid":7715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"算了"},{"pid":"9f770dcc331af5a79f407680d184d63ad953ed03","tid":1079003